{"ja518":{"ja518:0.1":{"pli":"Jātaka ","html":"<article id='ja518'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"ja518:0.2":{"pli":"Tiṁsanipāta ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"ja518:0.3":{"pli":"Kiṁchandavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"ja518:0.4":{"pli":"8. Paṇḍaranāgarājajātaka ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"ja518:1.1":{"pli":"“Vikiṇṇavācaṁ aniguyha mantaṁ, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:1.2":{"pli":"Asaññataṁ aparicakkhitāraṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:1.3":{"pli":"Bhayaṁ tamanveti sayaṁ abodhaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:1.4":{"pli":"Nāgaṁ yathā paṇḍarakaṁ supaṇṇo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:2.1":{"pli":"Yo guyhamantaṁ parirakkhaṇeyyaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:2.2":{"pli":"Mohā naro saṁsati hāsamāno; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:2.3":{"pli":"Taṁ bhinnamantaṁ bhayamanveti khippaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:2.4":{"pli":"Nāgaṁ yathā paṇḍarakaṁ supaṇṇo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:3.1":{"pli":"Nānumitto garuṁ atthaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:3.2":{"pli":"guyhaṁ veditumarahati; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:3.3":{"pli":"Sumitto ca asambuddhaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:3.4":{"pli":"sambuddhaṁ vā anatthavā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:4.1":{"pli":"Vissāsamāpajjimahaṁ acelaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:4.2":{"pli":"Samaṇo ayaṁ sammato bhāvitatto; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:4.3":{"pli":"Tassāhamakkhiṁ vivariṁ guyhamatthaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:4.4":{"pli":"Atītamattho kapaṇaṁ rudāmi. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:5.1":{"pli":"Tassāhaṁ paramaṁ brahme guyhaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:5.2":{"pli":"Vācañhi maṁ nāsakkhiṁ saṁyametuṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:5.3":{"pli":"Tappakkhato hi bhayamāgataṁ mamaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:5.4":{"pli":"Atītamattho kapaṇaṁ rudāmi. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:6.1":{"pli":"Yo ve naro suhadaṁ maññamāno, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:6.2":{"pli":"Guyhamatthaṁ saṁsati dukkulīne; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:6.3":{"pli":"Dosā bhayā athavā rāgarattā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:6.4":{"pli":"Pallatthito bālo asaṁsayaṁ so. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:7.1":{"pli":"Tirokkhavāco asataṁ paviṭṭho, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:7.2":{"pli":"Yo saṅgatīsu mudīreti vākyaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:7.3":{"pli":"Āsīviso dummukhotyāhu taṁ naraṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:7.4":{"pli":"Ārā ārā saṁyame tādisamhā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:8.1":{"pli":"Annaṁ pānaṁ kāsikacandanañca, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:8.2":{"pli":"Manāpitthiyo mālamucchādanañca; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:8.3":{"pli":"Ohāya gacchāmase sabbakāme, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:8.4":{"pli":"Supaṇṇa pāṇūpagatāva tyamhā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:9.1":{"pli":"“Ko nīdha tiṇṇaṁ garahaṁ upeti, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:9.2":{"pli":"Asmiṁdhaloke pāṇabhū nāgarāja; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:9.3":{"pli":"Samaṇo supaṇṇo athavā tvameva, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:9.4":{"pli":"Kiṁ kāraṇā paṇḍarakaggahīto”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:10.1":{"pli":"“Samaṇoti me sammatatto ahosi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:10.2":{"pli":"Piyo ca me manasā bhāvitatto; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:10.3":{"pli":"Tassāhamakkhiṁ vivariṁ guyhamatthaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:10.4":{"pli":"Atītamattho kapaṇaṁ rudāmi”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:11.1":{"pli":"“Na catthi satto amaro pathabyā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:11.2":{"pli":"Paññāvidhā natthi na ninditabbā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:11.3":{"pli":"Saccena dhammena dhitiyā damena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:11.4":{"pli":"Alabbhamabyāharatī naro idha. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:12.1":{"pli":"Mātāpitā paramā bandhavānaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:12.2":{"pli":"Nāssa tatiyo anukampakatthi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:12.3":{"pli":"Tesampi guyhaṁ paramaṁ na saṁse, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:12.4":{"pli":"Mantassa bhedaṁ parisaṅkamāno. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:13.1":{"pli":"Mātāpitā bhaginī bhātaro ca, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:13.2":{"pli":"Sahāyā vā yassa honti sapakkhā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:13.3":{"pli":"Tesampi guyhaṁ paramaṁ na saṁse, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:13.4":{"pli":"Mantassa bhedaṁ parisaṅkamāno. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:14.1":{"pli":"Bhariyā ce purisaṁ vajjā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:14.2":{"pli":"Komārī piyabhāṇinī; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:14.3":{"pli":"Puttarūpayasūpetā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:14.4":{"pli":"Ñātisaṅghapurakkhatā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:14.5":{"pli":"Tassāpi guyhaṁ paramaṁ na saṁse, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:14.6":{"pli":"Mantassa bhedaṁ parisaṅkamāno. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:15.1":{"pli":"Na guyhamatthaṁ vivareyya, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:15.2":{"pli":"Rakkheyya naṁ yathā nidhiṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:15.3":{"pli":"Na hi pātukato sādhu, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:15.4":{"pli":"Guyho attho pajānatā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:16.1":{"pli":"Thiyā guyhaṁ na saṁseyya, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:16.2":{"pli":"amittassa ca paṇḍito; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:16.3":{"pli":"Yo cāmisena saṁhīro, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:16.4":{"pli":"hadayattheno ca yo naro. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:17.1":{"pli":"Guyhamatthaṁ asambuddhaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:17.2":{"pli":"sambodhayati yo naro; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:17.3":{"pli":"Mantabhedabhayā tassa, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:17.4":{"pli":"dāsabhūto titikkhati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:18.1":{"pli":"Yāvanto purisassatthaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:18.2":{"pli":"guyhaṁ jānanti mantinaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:18.3":{"pli":"Tāvanto tassa ubbegā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:18.4":{"pli":"tasmā guyhaṁ na vissaje. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:19.1":{"pli":"Vivicca bhāseyya divā rahassaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:19.2":{"pli":"Rattiṁ giraṁ nātivelaṁ pamuñce; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:19.3":{"pli":"Upassutikā hi suṇanti mantaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:19.4":{"pli":"Tasmā manto khippamupeti bhedaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:20.1":{"pli":"Yathāpi assa nagaraṁ mahantaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:20.2":{"pli":"Advārakaṁ āyasaṁ bhaddasālaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:20.3":{"pli":"Samantakhātāparikhāupetaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:20.4":{"pli":"Evampi me te idha guyhamantā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:21.1":{"pli":"Ye guyhamantā avikiṇṇavācā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:21.2":{"pli":"Daḷhā sadatthesu narā dujivha; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:21.3":{"pli":"Ārā amittā byavajanti tehi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:21.4":{"pli":"Āsīvisā vā riva sattusaṅghā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:22.1":{"pli":"“Hitvā gharaṁ pabbajito acelo, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:22.2":{"pli":"Naggo muṇḍo carati ghāsahetu; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:22.3":{"pli":"Tamhi nu kho vivariṁ guyhamatthaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:22.4":{"pli":"Atthā ca dhammā ca apaggatamhā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:23.1":{"pli":"Kathaṅkaro hoti supaṇṇarāja, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:23.2":{"pli":"Kiṁsīlo kena vatena vattaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:23.3":{"pli":"Samaṇo caraṁ hitvā mamāyitāni, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:23.4":{"pli":"Kathaṅkaro saggamupeti ṭhānaṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:24.1":{"pli":"“Hiriyā titikkhāya damenupeto, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:24.2":{"pli":"Akkodhano pesuṇiyaṁ pahāya; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:24.3":{"pli":"Samaṇo caraṁ hitvā mamāyitāni, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:24.4":{"pli":"Evaṅkaro saggamupeti ṭhānaṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:25.1":{"pli":"“Mātāva puttaṁ taruṇaṁ tanujjaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:25.2":{"pli":"Samphassatā sabbagattaṁ phareti; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:25.3":{"pli":"Evampi me tvaṁ pāturahu dijinda, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:25.4":{"pli":"Mātāva puttaṁ anukampamāno”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:26.1":{"pli":"“Handajja tvaṁ muñca vadhā dujivha, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:26.2":{"pli":"Tayo hi puttā na hi añño atthi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:26.3":{"pli":"Antevāsī dinnako atrajo ca, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:26.4":{"pli":"Rajjassu puttaññataro me ahosi”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:27.1":{"pli":"Icceva vākyaṁ visajjī supaṇṇo, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:27.2":{"pli":"Bhumyaṁ patiṭṭhāya dijo dujivhaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:27.3":{"pli":"“Muttajja tvaṁ sabbabhayātivatto, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:27.4":{"pli":"Thalūdake hohi mayābhigutto. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:28.1":{"pli":"Ātaṅkinaṁ yathā kusalo bhisakko, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:28.2":{"pli":"Pipāsitānaṁ rahadova sīto; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:28.3":{"pli":"Vesmaṁ yathā himasītaṭṭitānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:28.4":{"pli":"Evampi te saraṇamahaṁ bhavāmi”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:29.1":{"pli":"“Sandhiṁ katvā amittena, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:29.2":{"pli":"aṇḍajena jalābuja; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:29.3":{"pli":"Vivariya dāṭhaṁ sesi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:29.4":{"pli":"kuto taṁ bhayamāgataṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:30.1":{"pli":"“Saṅketheva amittasmiṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:30.2":{"pli":"mittasmimpi na vissase; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:30.3":{"pli":"Abhayā bhayamuppannaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:30.4":{"pli":"api mūlāni kantati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:31.1":{"pli":"Kathaṁ nu vissase tyamhi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:31.2":{"pli":"yenāsi kalaho kato; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:31.3":{"pli":"Niccayattena ṭhātabbaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:31.4":{"pli":"so disabbhi na rajjati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:32.1":{"pli":"Vissāsaye na ca taṁ vissayeyya, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:32.2":{"pli":"Asaṅkito saṅkito ca bhaveyya; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:32.3":{"pli":"Tathā tathā viññū parakkameyya, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:32.4":{"pli":"Yathā yathā bhāvaṁ paro na jaññā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:33.1":{"pli":"Te devavaṇṇā sukhumālarūpā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:33.2":{"pli":"Ubho samā sujayā puññakhandhā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:33.3":{"pli":"Upāgamuṁ karampiyaṁ acelaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:33.4":{"pli":"Missībhūtā assavāhāva nāgā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:34.1":{"pli":"Tato have paṇḍarako acelaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:34.2":{"pli":"Sayamevupāgamma idaṁ avoca; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:34.3":{"pli":"“Muttajjahaṁ sabbabhayātivatto, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:34.4":{"pli":"Na hi nūna tuyhaṁ manaso piyamhā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:35.1":{"pli":"“Piyo hi me āsi supaṇṇarājā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:35.2":{"pli":"Asaṁsayaṁ paṇḍarakena saccaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:35.3":{"pli":"So rāgarattova akāsimetaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:35.4":{"pli":"Pāpakammaṁ sampajāno na mohā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:36.1":{"pli":"“Na me piyaṁ appiyaṁ vāpi hoti, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:36.2":{"pli":"Sampassato lokamimaṁ parañca; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:36.3":{"pli":"Susaññatānañhi viyañjanena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:36.4":{"pli":"Asaññato lokamimaṁ carāsi. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:37.1":{"pli":"Ariyāvakāsosi anariyovāsi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:37.2":{"pli":"Asaññato saññatasannikāso; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:37.3":{"pli":"Kaṇhābhijātikosi anariyarūpo, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:37.4":{"pli":"Pāpaṁ bahuṁ duccaritaṁ acāri. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:38.1":{"pli":"Aduṭṭhassa tuvaṁ dubbhi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:38.2":{"pli":"dubbhī ca pisuṇo casi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:38.3":{"pli":"Etena saccavajjena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:38.4":{"pli":"muddhā te phalatu sattadhā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja518:39.1":{"pli":"“Tasmā hi mittānaṁ na dubbhitabbaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:39.2":{"pli":"Mittadubbhā pāpiyo natthi añño; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:39.3":{"pli":"Āsittasatto nihato pathabyā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja518:39.4":{"pli":"Indassa vākyena hi saṁvaro hato”ti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"ja518:40.1":{"pli":"Paṇḍaranāgarājajātakaṁ aṭṭhamaṁ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"ja519":{"ja519:0.1":{"pli":"Jātaka ","html":"<article id='ja519'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"ja519:0.2":{"pli":"Tiṁsanipāta ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"ja519:0.3":{"pli":"Kiṁchandavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"ja519:0.4":{"pli":"9. Sambulājātaka ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"ja519:1.1":{"pli":"“Kā vedhamānā girikandarāyaṁ, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:1.2":{"pli":"Ekā tuvaṁ tiṭṭhasi saṁhitūru; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:1.3":{"pli":"Puṭṭhāsi me pāṇipameyyamajjhe, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:1.4":{"pli":"Akkhāhi me nāmañca bandhave ca. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:2.1":{"pli":"Obhāsayaṁ vanaṁ rammaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:2.2":{"pli":"sīhabyagghanisevitaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:2.3":{"pli":"Kā vā tvamasi kalyāṇi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:2.4":{"pli":"kassa vā tvaṁ sumajjhime; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:2.5":{"pli":"Abhivādemi taṁ bhadde, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:2.6":{"pli":"dānavāhaṁ namatthu te”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:3.1":{"pli":"“Yo putto kāsirājassa, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:3.2":{"pli":"sotthisenoti taṁ vidū; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:3.3":{"pli":"Tassāhaṁ sambulā bhariyā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:3.4":{"pli":"evaṁ jānāhi dānava; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:3.5":{"pli":"Abhivādemi taṁ bhante, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:3.6":{"pli":"sambulāhaṁ namatthu te. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:4.1":{"pli":"Vedehaputto bhaddante, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:4.2":{"pli":"vane vasati āturo; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:4.3":{"pli":"Tamahaṁ rogasammattaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:4.4":{"pli":"ekā ekaṁ upaṭṭhahaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:5.1":{"pli":"Ahañca vanamuñchāya, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:5.2":{"pli":"Madhumaṁsaṁ migābilaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:5.3":{"pli":"Yadāharāmi taṁ bhakkho, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:5.4":{"pli":"Tassa nūnajja nādhati”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:6.1":{"pli":"“Kiṁ vane rājaputtena, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:6.2":{"pli":"āturena karissasi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:6.3":{"pli":"Sambule pariciṇṇena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:6.4":{"pli":"ahaṁ bhattā bhavāmi te”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:7.1":{"pli":"“Sokaṭṭāya durattāya, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:7.2":{"pli":"kiṁ rūpaṁ vijjate mama; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:7.3":{"pli":"Aññaṁ pariyesa bhaddante, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:7.4":{"pli":"abhirūpataraṁ mayā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:8.1":{"pli":"“Ehimaṁ girimāruyha, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:8.2":{"pli":"bhariyā me catussatā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:8.3":{"pli":"Tāsaṁ tvaṁ pavarā hohi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:8.4":{"pli":"sabbakāmasamiddhinī. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:9.1":{"pli":"Nūna tārakavaṇṇābhe, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:9.2":{"pli":"yaṁ kiñci manasicchasi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:9.3":{"pli":"Sabbaṁ taṁ pacuraṁ mayhaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:9.4":{"pli":"ramassvajja mayā saha. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:10.1":{"pli":"No ce tuvaṁ maheseyyaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:10.2":{"pli":"Sambule kārayissasi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:10.3":{"pli":"Alaṁ tvaṁ pātarāsāya, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:10.4":{"pli":"Paṇhe bhakkhā bhavissasi”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:11.1":{"pli":"Tañca sattajaṭo luddo, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:11.2":{"pli":"kaḷāro purisādako; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:11.3":{"pli":"Vane nāthaṁ apassantiṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:11.4":{"pli":"sambulaṁ aggahī bhuje. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:12.1":{"pli":"Adhipannā pisācena, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:12.2":{"pli":"luddenāmisacakkhunā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:12.3":{"pli":"Sā ca sattuvasaṁ pattā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:12.4":{"pli":"patimevānusocati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:13.1":{"pli":"“Na me idaṁ tathā dukkhaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:13.2":{"pli":"yaṁ maṁ khādeyya rakkhaso; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:13.3":{"pli":"Yañca me ayyaputtassa, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:13.4":{"pli":"mano hessati aññathā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:14.1":{"pli":"Na santi devā pavasanti nūna, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:14.2":{"pli":"Na hi nūna santi idha lokapālā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:14.3":{"pli":"Sahasā karontānamasaññatānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:14.4":{"pli":"Na hi nūna santi paṭisedhitāro”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:15.1":{"pli":"“Itthīnamesā pavarā yasassinī, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:15.2":{"pli":"Santā samā aggirivuggatejā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:15.3":{"pli":"Tañce tuvaṁ rakkhasādesi kaññaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:15.4":{"pli":"Muddhā ca hi sattadhā te phaleyya; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:15.5":{"pli":"Mā tvaṁ dahī muñca patibbatāya”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:16.1":{"pli":"Sā ca assamamāgacchi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:16.2":{"pli":"pamuttā purisādakā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:16.3":{"pli":"Nīḷaṁ paḷinaṁ sakuṇīva, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:16.4":{"pli":"gatasiṅgaṁva ālayaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:17.1":{"pli":"Sā tattha paridevesi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:17.2":{"pli":"rājaputtī yasassinī; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:17.3":{"pli":"Sambulā utumattakkhā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:17.4":{"pli":"vane nāthaṁ apassantī. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:18.1":{"pli":"Samaṇe brāhmaṇe vande, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:18.2":{"pli":"sampannacaraṇe ise; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:18.3":{"pli":"Rājaputtaṁ apassantī, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:18.4":{"pli":"“tumhaṁmhi saraṇaṁ gatā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:19.1":{"pli":"Vande sīhe ca byagghe ca, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:19.2":{"pli":"ye ca aññe vane migā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:19.3":{"pli":"Rājaputtaṁ apassantī, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:19.4":{"pli":"“tumhaṁmhi saraṇaṁ gatā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:20.1":{"pli":"Tiṇā latāni osadhyo, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:20.2":{"pli":"pabbatāni vanāni ca; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:20.3":{"pli":"Rājaputtaṁ apassantī, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:20.4":{"pli":"“tumhaṁmhi saraṇaṁ gatā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:21.1":{"pli":"Vande indīvarīsāmaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:21.2":{"pli":"rattiṁ nakkhattamāliniṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:21.3":{"pli":"Rājaputtaṁ apassantī, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:21.4":{"pli":"“tumhaṁmhi saraṇaṁ gatā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:22.1":{"pli":"Vande bhāgīrathiṁ gaṅgaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:22.2":{"pli":"savantīnaṁ paṭiggahaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:22.3":{"pli":"Rājaputtaṁ apassantī, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:22.4":{"pli":"“tumhaṁmhi saraṇaṁ gatā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:23.1":{"pli":"Vande ahaṁ pabbatarājaseṭṭhaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:23.2":{"pli":"Himavantaṁ siluccayaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:23.3":{"pli":"Rājaputtaṁ apassantī, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:23.4":{"pli":"“Tumhaṁmhi saraṇaṁ gatā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:24.1":{"pli":"“Atisāyaṁ vatāgacchi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:24.2":{"pli":"rājaputti yasassini; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:24.3":{"pli":"Kena nujja samāgacchi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:24.4":{"pli":"ko te piyataro mayā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:25.1":{"pli":"“Idaṁ khohaṁ tadāvocaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:25.2":{"pli":"gahitā tena sattunā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:25.3":{"pli":"Na me idaṁ tathā dukkhaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:25.4":{"pli":"yaṁ maṁ khādeyya rakkhaso; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:25.5":{"pli":"Yañca me ayyaputtassa, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:25.6":{"pli":"mano hessati aññathā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:26.1":{"pli":"“Corīnaṁ bahubuddhīnaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:26.2":{"pli":"yāsu saccaṁ sudullabhaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:26.3":{"pli":"Thīnaṁ bhāvo durājāno, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:26.4":{"pli":"macchassevodake gataṁ”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:27.1":{"pli":"“Tathā maṁ saccaṁ pāletu, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:27.2":{"pli":"pālayissati ce mamaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:27.3":{"pli":"Yathāhaṁ nābhijānāmi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:27.4":{"pli":"aññaṁ piyataraṁ tayā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:27.5":{"pli":"Etena saccavajjena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:27.6":{"pli":"byādhi te vūpasammatu”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:28.1":{"pli":"“Ye kuñjarā sattasatā uḷārā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:28.2":{"pli":"Rakkhanti rattindivamuyyutāvudhā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:28.3":{"pli":"Dhanuggahānañca satāni soḷasa, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:28.4":{"pli":"Kathaṁvidhe passasi bhadde sattavo”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:29.1":{"pli":"“Alaṅkatāyo padumuttarattacā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:29.2":{"pli":"Virāgitā passati haṁsagaggarā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:29.3":{"pli":"Tāsaṁ suṇitvā mitagītavāditaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:29.4":{"pli":"Na dāni me tāta tathā yathā pure. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:30.1":{"pli":"Suvaṇṇasaṅkaccadharā suviggahā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:30.2":{"pli":"Alaṅkatā mānusiyaccharūpamā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:30.3":{"pli":"Senopiyā tāta aninditaṅgiyo, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:30.4":{"pli":"Khattiyakaññā paṭilobhayanti naṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:31.1":{"pli":"Sace ahaṁ tāta tathā yathā pure, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:31.2":{"pli":"Patiṁ tamuñchāya punā vane bhare; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:31.3":{"pli":"Sammānaye maṁ na ca maṁ vimānaye, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:31.4":{"pli":"Itopi me tāta tato varaṁ siyā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:32.1":{"pli":"Yamannapāne vipulasmi ohite, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:32.2":{"pli":"Nārī vimaṭṭhābharaṇā alaṅkatā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:32.3":{"pli":"Sabbaṅgupetā patino ca appiyā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:32.4":{"pli":"Abajjha tassā maraṇaṁ tato varaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:33.1":{"pli":"Api ce daliddā kapaṇā anāḷhiyā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:33.2":{"pli":"Kaṭādutīyā patino ca sā piyā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:33.3":{"pli":"Sabbaṅgupetāyapi appiyāya, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:33.4":{"pli":"Ayameva seyyā kapaṇāpi yā piyā”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:34.1":{"pli":"“Sudullabhitthī purisassa yā hitā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:34.2":{"pli":"Bhattitthiyā dullabho yo hito ca; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:34.3":{"pli":"Hitā ca te sīlavatī ca bhariyā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:34.4":{"pli":"Janinda dhammaṁ cara sambulāya”. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"ja519:35.1":{"pli":"“Sace tuvaṁ vipule laddhabhoge, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:35.2":{"pli":"Issāvatiṇṇā maraṇaṁ upesi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:35.3":{"pli":"Ahañca te bhadde imā rājakaññā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja519:35.4":{"pli":"Sabbe te vacanakarā bhavāmā”ti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"ja519:36.1":{"pli":"Sambulājātakaṁ navamaṁ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"ja52":{"ja52:0.1":{"pli":"Jātaka ","eng":"Stories of Past Lives 52 ","html":"<article id='ja52'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"ja52:0.2":{"pli":"Ekakanipāta ","eng":"The Book of the Ones ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"ja52:0.3":{"pli":"Āsīsavagga ","eng":"Hope ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"ja52:0.4":{"pli":"2. Cūḷajanakajātaka ","eng":"A Short Tale of Janaka: a past life story ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"ja52:1.1":{"pli":"“Vāyametheva puriso, ","eng":"A man should make an effort ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>","comm":"The story, which is told in full in the Mahājanakajātaka <a href='index.html?q=ja539'>Ja 539</a>, relates how Janaka of Videha regained his kingdom through unremitting effort. | The Janakas were the famed kingly house of Videha. At <a href='index.html?q=mn83#20.1'>MN 83:20.1</a> a Janaka is framed as the source of the kingdom’s decline. A King Janaka was Sītā’s father in the Rāmāyaṇa, and one discussed philosophy with Yājñavalkya in the Bṛhadāraṇyaka Upaniṣad. It seems impossible to determine which, if any, are the same person. "},"ja52:1.2":{"pli":"na nibbindeyya paṇḍito; ","eng":"the astute should not be disillusioned. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"ja52:1.3":{"pli":"Passāmi vohaṁ attānaṁ, ","eng":"Now I truly see myself, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>","comm":"For these lines, compare <a href='index.html?q=thag1.88'>Thag 1.88</a>. "},"ja52:1.4":{"pli":"udakā thalamubbhatan”ti. ","eng":"lifted from the water to the shore. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>","comm":"The story of Ja 539 relates how he survived the sinking of his ship. "},"ja52:2.1":{"pli":"Cūḷajanakajātakaṁ dutiyaṁ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}}}